data.description: Drive up to your fantastic custom home on two acres of serene land. Deer and other friendly animals come to graze on the yard and take shade under the trees. Home is equipped with its own private observation deck. Walk over a short bridge towards the front door and enter into a space for the cook of the family and space to visit and enjoy time together as well. Large bedrooms for extra comfort. This home is gorgeous and a must see! Call today for an appointment.
